Interface IDataSegmentIterator.IDataSegmentChunk

  • Enclosing interface:
    IDataSegmentIterator

    public static interface IDataSegmentIterator.IDataSegmentChunk

    IDataSegmentChunk

    This class represents a chunk of a data segment, which is sent with a Protocol Data Unit.
